{"title":"linux修改dns","date":"2022-01-16T09:36:15.015Z","source":"_posts/linux修改dns.md","raw":"---\ntitle: linux修改dns\ndate: 2022-01-16 17:36:15.015\nupdated: 2022-01-16 17:36:15.015\ncategories: \ntags: \n- linux\n---\nlinux修改dns\n<!-- more -->\n# linux修改dns\nifconfig -a\n一般来说，eth0就是第一块网卡了，而lo是localhost的缩写。\n\n然后编辑 /etc/network/interfaces  添加下面的信息\n```shell\nauto eth0\t\t// 开机自动挂载这张网卡\niface eth0 inet static\t// 使用静态ip\naddress 192.168.1.233\nnetmask 255.255.255.0\ngateway 192.168.1.1\n```\n\n如果使用DHCP，将\"iface eth0 inte static\"改为\"iface eth0 inet dhcp\"\n\n配置DNS服务器\n\n编辑/etc/resolv.conf\n\nnameserver 114.114.114.114\n\n然后重启机器或者重启网卡，附上重启网卡的指令:\n\n/etc/init.d/networking restart\n","slug":"linux修改dns","published":true,"updated":"2022-01-16T09:36:15.015Z","_id":"cm833960t000zi0q6fped4bwo","comments":true,"layout":"post","photos":[],"html":"<p>linux修改dns</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h1 id=\"linux修改dns\"><a href=\"#linux修改dns\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"linux修改dns\"></a>linux修改dns</h1><p>ifconfig -a<br>一般来说，eth0就是第一块网卡了，而lo是localhost的缩写。</p>\n<p>然后编辑 &#x2F;etc&#x2F;network&#x2F;interfaces  添加下面的信息</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">auto eth0\t\t// 开机自动挂载这张网卡</span><br><span class=\"line\">iface eth0 inet static\t// 使用静态ip</span><br><span class=\"line\">address 192.168.1.233</span><br><span class=\"line\">netmask 255.255.255.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">gateway 192.168.1.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>如果使用DHCP，将”iface eth0 inte static”改为”iface eth0 inet dhcp”</p>\n<p>配置DNS服务器</p>\n<p>编辑&#x2F;etc&#x2F;resolv.conf</p>\n<p>nameserver 114.114.114.114</p>\n<p>然后重启机器或者重启网卡，附上重启网卡的指令:</p>\n<p>&#x2F;etc&#x2F;init.d&#x2F;networking restart</p>\n","excerpt":"<p>linux修改dns</p>","more":"<h1 id=